metadata.name: TIME TRAVELER #1
metadata.description:
We are not alone, we are all ONE.

Time Traveler depicts a soul, an expression of infinite Universal Consciousness, always present throughout time and space. A different person, a different face, each Time Traveler is unique and interconnected as ONE.

Hand-drawn original art by Sarkis Delimelkon also known as SARKISM using Procreate app on an iPad Pro. Created intuitively, in an energetically charged flow-state, without visual reference.

TIME TRAVELER #1 is the first digital B&W 1/1 Time Traveler

Dimensions:  
7000px X 7000px 300dpi  
10.4MB
